partea superioara stanga a spatelui,

593
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:33,350
dupa ce a trecut prin inima.

594
00:37:33,350 --> 00:37:38,590
Arma este aproape o chestie ascutita, cilindrica,

595
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:41,369
dura, cu un varf, ca un...

596
00:37:41,369 --> 00:37:43,370
Cum ar fi asta.

597
00:37:43,370 --> 00:37:45,469
Da, asa e.

598
00:37:45,470 --> 00:37:47,070
Oh, nu!

